description:
Welcome to the Houston Texans App, your main access point for tickets, exclusive giveaways, news, and Texans content!

Use the Texans app to make every day feel like gameday:

- Mobile ticketing with personalized navigation;
- Exclusive giveaways from the Texans and our partners;
- Custom App Icons, including our H logo and the H-Town Blue bullhead logo;
- The latest Ticketmaster updates for a smooth gameday experience;
- Mobile ordering opportunities for specific seating locations, and easy-access merch and concessions discounts for Season Ticket Members!
